&lt;p&gt;Added BOOLEAN to the appropriate metadata query.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;-------------&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;M      java/testing/org/apache/derbyTesting/functionTests/tests/lang/BooleanValuesTest.java&lt;br/&gt;
M      java/testing/org/apache/derbyTesting/functionTests/tests/lang/CastingTest.java&lt;br/&gt;
M      java/testing/org/apache/derbyTesting/functionTests/tests/lang/UDTTest.java&lt;br/&gt;
M      java/testing/org/apache/derbyTesting/functionTests/tests/jdbcapi/DatabaseMetaDataTest.java&lt;br/&gt;
M      java/testing/org/apache/derbyTesting/functionTests/master/connectionJdbc20.out&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Adjusted tests to account for the new datatype.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
